Experiments:

In main : 

exp1 should be executed for different parameters. It is reflected in :

TestParams params = {dbName, dbSize, 5, 1, 100000, 4'000'000, 3};

in this case 5 is an Bloom filter hierqarchy order and 4M is a Bloom filter size.

It was tested for: (5, 4M), (3, 4M), (5, 2M), (5, 1M)

Running for the first parameter set creates all databases.

